{"type": "article", "id": 10002, "title": "Andy Warhol & Retrosuperfuture 太阳镜", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-26T07:24:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235405CuUVQWLOfzHkea8v.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tAndy Warhol 最近和意大利眼镜品牌 Retrosuperfuture 联合推出了四款新的太阳镜，分别命名为BabyBaby、Nicolou、VelvetDarling 和 Ultracandy，这些都是常常出入 Andy Warhol 工作室的朋友的名字，而在造型上，有红色心形，猫眼镜框配黑色镜片等个性十足的设计。产品将会在6月份登陆线上和线下门店，<a href=\"http://retrosuperfuture.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235403rlqm7HIgd0W6sfQt.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235403lfj63diatTNABWoM.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354047X5FnkwuKUqN0dT3.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354047FfnrH9a8ITSlept.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}